title: The Rabbit Hole
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Cafe and bar inside Hotel Villa, next to the Saka ski lifts. Offers barista made espresso coffee (has soy milk) and a range of food. The veggie burger is a house-made sweet potato patty (vegan) served on a toasted bun with hummus and salad. The Mexican loaded fries can be adapted to be vegan (ask to omit cheese). Specify you want vegan just to be sure.
